description: Greek yoghurt makes this healthier wholemeal muffins super moist and fluffy.
keywords: Sweet muffin,Pescatarian,Seafood free,Blueberry,Soy free,Vegetarian,Tree nut free,Egg,Sesame free,Peanut free
name: Wholemeal Blueberry & Yoghurt Muffins Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat the oven to 190°C/170°C fan-forced and line a muffin pan with 12 paper cases.
Whisk the flour, baking powder, baking soda and cinnamon together in a large bowl. Mix the wet ingredients together in a bowl, pour into the dry ingredients and gently mix to combine.

Stir in the blueberries, reserving a small handful. Scoop the batter into the muffin cases, top each muffin with blueberries and bake for 1820 minutes until golden. Cool for 10 minutes on a wire rack and serve.
